  » </strong> Software Engineering  — </strong></strong> Ph.D.   l   M.S.     
  » </strong> Statistics  — </strong></strong> Ph.D.   l   M.S.  
   » </strong>Information &amp; Computer Science (Informatics  Concentration)</strong>  — </strong></strong> M.S.     
  » </strong> Information &amp; Computer Science </strong> ( Embedded Systems </strong>Concentration)   — </strong></strong> M.S.   The Embedded Systems Concentration is not currently open for enrollment.  
